NGR Mechanic
The New German Republic Mechanic is a technical specialist responsible for
maintaining the NGR's combat robots, power armor, vehicles, and weapon
systems. In a nation fighting on multiple fronts, a mechanic who can keep
equipment running under fire is as valuable as any soldier.

NGR Mechanics choose from Technical, Electrical, and Physical skill
categories. Their mechanical and electronic skills are exceptional and they
are trained to work on both conventional and alien-derived technology captured
from Gargoyle forces.

Attribute requirements: IQ 11.
Starting equipment: NGR field coveralls, basic tool kit, computer pad, personal
radio, one sidearm, and standard maintenance supplies.
